OL,3,CITV Channel Weather Watch: Will we get
OL,4,Ca white Christmas?
OL,6,FIt's beginning to look a lot like...
OL,7,FDecember!
OL,9,FChristmas is just around the corner
OL,10,Fand winter is well on its way.
OL,12,FFestive greetings cards show snow-
OL,13,Fcapped villages and icy wonderlands.
OL,14,FBut in reality, how common is a white
OL,15,FChristmas in the Channel Islands?
OL,17,FRead on to find the answer to all of
OL,18,Fyour wintery weather musings.
OL,20,FDecember weather trends
