OL,3,CITV Channel Weather Watch: Will we get
OL,4,Ca white Christmas?
OL,6,FDecember is characterised by shorter
OL,7,Fdays and often wet and windy weather.
OL,9,FIt is also one of the chillier months
OL,10,Fof the year.
OL,12,FShorter daylight hours and more cloud
OL,13,Fcover mean less sunshine - just over
OL,14,Ftwo hours a day on average in December
OL,15,F- giving us colder days and chillier
OL,16,Fnights.
OL,18,FLast year in Guernsey, nine days saw
OL,19,Fno sunshine at all.
