OL,3,CITV Channel Weather Watch: Will we get
OL,4,Ca white Christmas?
OL,6,FDecember can therefore feel noticeably
OL,7,Fcolder than November or October.
OL,9,FHowever, the sea is still relatively
OL,10,Fmild at this time of year, which
OL,11,Fmitigates temperature cooling. This
OL,12,Fmeans December is rarely as cold as
OL,13,FJanuary or February.
OL,15,FA white Christmas is rare, but a wet
OL,16,Fone is more common.
OL,18,FOn average, December sees around 4mm
OL,19,Fof rain daily, making it the rainiest
OL,20,Fmonth of the year.
