OL,6,FBlustery winds and storms can persist
OL,7,Finto December.
OL,9,FLow-pressure systems run over us more
OL,10,Ffrequently as the jet stream sits
OL,11,Ffurther south in the winter, bringing
OL,12,Fus more wind, rain, and clouds.
