OL,3,CITV Channel Weather Watch: Will we get
OL,4,Ca white Christmas?
OL,6,FDecember marks the start of the winter
OL,7,Fmonths, though the precise date
OL,8,Fdepends on your definition.
OL,10,FFor meteorologists, winter begins on 1
OL,11,FDecember.
OL,13,FThe date coincides with the start of
OL,14,Fthe month to make it easier to compare
OL,15,Fweather and climate data across months
OL,16,Fand years.
OL,18,FAstronomical winter, however, begins
OL,19,Fon 21 December - at the point when the
OL,20,FSun is exactly overhead the Tropic of
OL,21,FCapricorn.
